creator: Signify Netherlands B.V.
descriptionHtml:
Powered by the Interact Indoor Navigation technology, it features advanced lighting and temperature controls based on user’s location.
The app is intended to boost productivity and improve engagement of occupants by handing control over the workspace environment. Customizing your workplace

Set up your location
To enable features such as light or temperature control, selecting your location is required.

1. Select your site, building and tap Continue.
2. Tap Allow access to grant access to your
location.
3. The available controls appear in the app’s home screen. You can start adjusting your lights and temperature.

Adjust the lights
Lights can be adjusted by selecting a preset in areas such as desks and meetings rooms where light control is enabled.
1. Tap Adjust the lights.
2. Select the desired preset for an area.
3. The light level changes based on the selected preset.

Adjust the temperature
Temperature can be adjusted by selecting the desired level for an area. The temperature can be adjusted either two steps up or down.
1. Tap Adjust the temperature.
2. Adjust the temperature to the desired level and Confirm.
3. You are notified if your request has been accepted and when the temperature is adjusted.
descriptionShort: The app enables occupants to customize comfort settings in their workplace.
